# THIS IS NOT A REAL KEY.
#
# Public key matching the private.pem used by auth-service for JWT signing.
# Generate the matching pair following the instructions in private.pem.example.
#
# This file is the canonical public key; consuming services
# (admin-service, community-service) must hold a copy of the SAME public key
# under their own apps/<service>/src/main/resources/keys/public.pem.
#
# When a key rotation happens in production, all three locations (and any
# other consumer added later) must be updated atomically.
